{"tid":1484551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真相］終於知道班大陸仔帶gear過關做咩，就係去金鐘！","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T06:10:37.000Z","uid":179648,"like":226,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7e342fe0306fad283ac5c06a38de19108cab98","tid":1484551,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"到呢一刻都可以咁多人聚集係金鐘，合理解釋就係佢地專登。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有大量可靠消息話有大陸仔帶gear黑衫過關，點解今日仲未出現？呢到講緊有過百人。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，之前已經有傳聞警察會派臥底留到最尾扮送頭，睇落多啲人被捕嚇你。如果你係警察，你會唔會今晚再出招？呢到都數以十計。<br />\n<br />\n今日吹到咁行和理非散水，我當你唔睇連登tg, 有落現場根本都聽到民陣/身邊嘅人叫散水啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔好屌我冷氣軍師笑前線，我啱啱先返到屋企洗完腳指。<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻仲喺現場嘅，幫手拉人走啦，求下你！"},{"pid":"ea7fd9c04f48212c7b62ffe6002c41154ee67982","tid":1484551,"uid":179648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"走啦求下你"},{"pid":"e2a1f8beec686163664539a7ac84b870a2733a68","tid":1484551,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"你走啦我唔想搞大佢"},{"pid":"62f4e4670e8707808864a3fe76dc4270e58f38db","tid":1484551,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"返屋企啦手足"},{"pid":"168ceeb374dbe6fd00e5b1722b8fc85e207e6b2c","tid":1484551,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"求下你走啦"},{"pid":"8a30fb9acb13a05fd81a763fddd5c30ce469df17","tid":1484551,"uid":74723,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:39.000Z","msg":"11點都唔走既就係大陸人，係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa52dd8e8e05bf281c2170e3a6720ce11163c5cd","tid":1484551,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"走啦求下你"},{"pid":"70c7e112db95804beed65830236fb75b41ce8ce6","tid":1484551,"uid